<topic id="preferences-xquery-saxon">
  <title>Saxon-HE/PE/EE Preferences</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Preferences<indexterm>Saxon-HE/PE/EE XQuery</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Saxon HE/PE/EE XQuery preferences</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_agq_bgk_54b">To configure global options for XQuery transformation and validation
      scenarios that use the <uicontrol>Saxon HE/PE/EE</uicontrol> engine, <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/> and go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>XML</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>XSLT-XQuery</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>XQuery</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Saxon-HE/PE/EE</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>.</p>
    <p id="p_bgq_bgk_54b"><ph keyref="product"/> allows you to configure the following XQuery options for the Saxon <ph
        keyref="saxon9FullVersion"/> Home Edition (HE), Professional Edition (PE), and Enterprise
      Edition (EE):<dl id="dl_cgq_bgk_54b">
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-use-config-file-" id="dlentry_dgq_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/optimization-level" id="optimization-level">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/linked-tree" id="dlentry_egq_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-strip-whitespaces-" id="dlentry_ggq_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
    <p id="p_hgq_bgk_54b">The following option is available for Saxon <ph keyref="saxon9FullVersion"/> Professional
      Edition (PE) and Enterprise Edition (EE) only:<dl id="dl_igq_bgk_54b">
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-allow-calls-" id="dlentry_jgq_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
    <p id="p_kgq_bgk_54b">The options available specifically for Saxon <ph keyref="saxon9FullVersion"/> Enterprise
      Edition (EE) are as follows:<dl id="dl_lgq_bgk_54b">
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-val-source-file-" id="dlentry_mgq_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/saxon-option-outval-" id="dlentry_ngq_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-enable-update-" id="dlentry_ogq_bgk_54b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry
          conref="../reusables/topics/reusables-querying-documents.dita#reusables-querying-documents/xquery-saxon-ee-advanced-options-end-"
          id="dlentry_it1_34v_z5b">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
